# Homelab server (Debian) — LAN + Tailscale
Host uruk uruk-ts
  User laublet
  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/uruk
  IdentitiesOnly yes
  ServerAliveInterval 60
  ServerAliveCountMax 3

Host uruk
  HostName 192.168.1.104

Host uruk-ts
  HostName uruk.tail6c9b30.ts.net

